name: Not for Dinner
description:
-Controls-

  • Hold Space to charge up jump
  • WASD to direct jump relative to camera
  • Mouse to rotate view

-About-

Fish out of water simulator! Get to the sink and flush you way to victory, and far away from the dinner plate!

Not for dinner was the winner for the 2019 world skills challenge for the Melbourne Australia region. The challenge was a game jam type scenario running for eight hours in teams of two.

Created by Yulia Yesova (Artstation) and Nathan Kelly
